                        <additions>
                            <p>
                                <locus from="LCI" to="LCI" scheme="other"/>
                                <note>Top right, in pencil by a modern hand: a note on the donation note on <locus from="222v" to="222v" scheme="folios"/>, <quote>Från Plessis-le-Tours i Frankrike; skänkt till därvarande kollegium af Ludvig XI's almoseutdelare magister Johannes Gareau</quote>; bottom right, in pencil by a modern hand: <quote>1695. f. 112 1698 f. 125</quote>.</note>
                            </p>
                        </additions>
                        <bindingDesc>
                            <binding contemporary="false">
                                <p>Early modern binding. Parchment over cardboard. 4 raised bands and endbands; endbands visible. 2 holes, back and front, for straps. <locus from="Spine" to="Spine" scheme="other"/>, in brown ink: <quote>Magister sententiarum</quote>; in pencil: <quote>Lombardus</quote>; in ink: <quote>26</quote>; stamped in gold: <quote>A 151</quote>; in ink on a paper label: <quote>e. 30. 3. 13.</quote>; visible in ink on the remnants of a paper label: <quote>XXVIII</quote>.</p>
                                <p>
